name: Utsumi Erice FGO
description:
Not much to say other than the usual information for this LORA.

The checkpoints used for the examples shown here are :

abyssorangemix3

AnythingV5

You don't need to put anything other than the keyword " FGOErice ", however there seems to be an inconsistency with the lower part of her outfit. I would really suggest you to add these tags if you want to generate a full-body image:

" leg warmers, sandals, heels " this last one also works but again, it's hit or miss so I would just generate the whole image and then inpaint it.

Trained using NAI so a lot of flexibility on checkpoints.

For weights anything lower than 0.5 it's just a miss, and interestingly it holds up nice at very high weights too, testing started on 0.5 and ended on 1.5

Recommendation would be to just stick to 1.0

Somehow Civitai won't show the complete image, so here's a link if you want to take a closer look

https://www.dropbox.com/s/6kiyc7d2ce648e2/Sample%20from%2005%20to%2015.jpg?dl=0

That's it, don't think I'm gonna do the summer version, if anything I would like to fix the problem with her footwear and the things she wears on her shins.

Thinking on maybe do Ritsuka (gudao) next.
